short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tracks your page visits to your WorkdayTracker account

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your productivity with the WorkdayTracker Chrome Extension. Seamlessly track and record the websites you visit, integrating them directly into your WorkdayTracker account. This extension helps you keep an accurate log of your online activity, ensuring that every page visit is documented for better time management and efficiency analysis.
